<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The stock of Berkshire Hathaway Inc., an Omaha
holding company run by billionaire takeover specialist Warren E.
Buffett, debuted Tuesday on the New York Stock Exchange.
   But at an opening price of $4,750 a common share only the
thick-skinned, thick-pursed investor need apply.
